<p>One unique feature of Book of Thieves is the additional box next to the third reel. It receives a symbol with every spin, giving players an extra chance to win big. It's like getting a bonus present every time you spin the reels - who doesn't love that?</p>

<p>Overall, Book of Thieves provides players with a fantastic game that combines low betting limits with a high maximum payout. So go forth, spin those reels, and remember to keep an eye on that additional box - it could just be your ticket to the big leagues.</p>"
